<center><table border=0><tr><td><center><H2><font face=arial>It will be in final, but what they are saying is unfair</font></H2></center>
<font face=arial size=2><b>Posted By:</b> <A HREF="/cgi-local/whois2.cgi?Tarquin">Tarquin</a><br>
<b>Posted On:</b> 2:31 p.m. 15/3/1999<br>
<b>Subject:</b> It will be in final, but what they are saying is unfair<p>
<br><center><img src="http://www.everworld.net/pvpquest/images/divider.gif" width=452 height=22 border=0></center><BR><P ALIGN=CENTER><b>In Reply To:</b> <A HREF="http://www.everworld.net/cgi-local/pvp.cgi?read=1413" TARGET=_self>I have no idea where you heard this but....</A> (Angus[CC])
</STRONG><FONT SIZE=2 color=#FFFFFF FACE=arial>
<P>> It's bullshit. PvP server will be up for final. Now, for it to

<BR>&gt; stay up we need to have a decent population in comparison to all
<BR>&gt; the other servers. I promise you that if all other server are
<BR>&gt; over crowded and we only have 500 people on our, they will take
<BR>&gt; it down. Thats just basic math. They won't allow every else to
<BR>&gt; suffer for a minority.
<P>I know it will be up but they said they will take it down if they dont meet their quota.. what the hell is this! We will lose our time and characters! I bet you other new servers that they will put that dont reach 500+ will stay... dont they realize some people will spend like 8 hours a day for a month before they take a server down?..
<P>Minority? suffer? what you mean everyone else suffer? whos gonna suffer?
<P>&gt; Therfor we must show our number, you must get all your friends
<BR>&gt; and your friends guilds to play the PvP server. Not just part
<BR>&gt; time, but with their main characters. Part time players are not
<BR>&gt; what will help us. We need to show how many of us there are. if
<BR>&gt; we do not then we have only ourselves to blame.
<P>I agree man, well its good that all of you CC will play, .. I and my friends will play as well, and i hear a lot of other old timers will play so thats at least 50-100 good players there... + in beta of 25,000 people about 15,000 played, and pvp had 150, so thats 100:1..ouch ..in final if there are 150,000 that play, pvp shard should have 1500 people on it. .( I'd hate to see that many players on it, I'd rather love the cap to be like 1000 or so..)
<P>
</FONT></td></tr></table></P>
